properties.name: dialogText
properties.value: Greetings, adventurer! I'm Farmer Joe, your go-to for all farming needs. Browse my selection of goods, sell any items you've gathered, or use the depot to store your belongings. And don't forget, I can grant you access to the marketplace to sell your bountiful harvests and resources from your farm. Happy farming!

properties.name: dialogText
properties.value:
Greetings! Elden Timberheart at your service. The woods are alive with the rustle of opportunity. With a carpenter's axe in hand, simply click on it, select 'Use With,' and target a tree trunk to harvest timber, one of the finest crafting materials around. Whether you turn it into wooden boards or sell it directly on the marketplace, timber is key for crafting essentials like arrows and bows. So, let's get chopping and make the most of these bountiful woods!

PS: You can craft a wooden board using your crafting menu!

properties.name: dialogText
properties.value:
Ahoy there, friend! You've come to the right place to cast your line. This lake's teeming with fish. Grab your fishing rod, and find a cozy spot. Click on it and set "Use With", then tap on the sea.

Remember you need worms to fish! These can be found on the Ilya village sewer rats. Just take the boat below.

I'll give you some so you can get started!

properties.name: dialogText
properties.value: Stranger, I am Ragnok Hornbreaker, once a proud guardian of labyrinths, now a seeker of justice within these cursed lands. Ironforge ahead is no longer a place of honorable toil but a labyrinth of greed, twisted by dwarves lost to envy and avarice. My brethren and I once respected their kind, but now, I ask you to challenge 15 of these corrupted souls. But be careful! These treachery dwarfs will stab you to death if you're not prepared! I advice you to go to Ilya's training room or sewers, to get some experience with harmless foes.

properties.name: dialogText
properties.value: Well met, traveler! Durgan Ironvein's my name, and mining's my game. These mountains are rich with ores just waiting to be uncovered. If you've got a pickaxe and a sturdy pair of hands, I can show you how to extract precious minerals. Just click on it, set "Use with" and then click on the stone. You'll start getting some ore! After this, use your blacksmith's hammer on the anvil to convert it to ingots! These are the basic crafting materials for gears. You can also sell this on the marketplace in Ilya city and get some gold!

properties.name: dialogText
properties.value: Ah, a visitor after such endless quiet! I am Mordecai, a practitioner of forbidden magics. I seek your aid in a grim task. Venture to the old graveyard and retrieve bones that rest beneath cold stones. With them, I shall attempt to resurrect my old friend, Sleemer. The spirits whisper of a chance to undo the past. Will you brave the shadows for me?
